-- Indonesia's Bank Mandiri posts 16 pct rise in H1 net profit
-- By Fathiyah Dahrul
-- Thu Jul 24, 2014 05:22AM EDT
-- None



JAKARTA, July 24 (Reuters) - Indonesia's PT Bank Mandiri <BMRI.JK> reported a 16 percent rise in first-half net profit on stronger net interest income and fee-based income.

